Manchester City forward Toni Duggan posted a photo with Manchester United manager Louis van Gaal at Wing's restaurant on Sunday night . 
  The 23-year-old has apologised on her Facebook page and removed the photo . 
  Duggan received a number of abusive messages on social media . 
  The Manchester City forward was with Van Gaal at the restaurant after United beat Manchester City 4-2 at Old Trafford . 
 